\pard\f0\fs28  Subgen.{\b  Anthelaea} (Griseb.) Buchenau. Perennials or annuals. Flowers usually in pairs, sometimes borne singly or in larger groups. Seeds with short to inconspicuous basal appendage or appendage absent.
